## Calibration Notes
- These thresholds are starting points — recalibrate after 30+ days of live data
- BTC 15min ATR_PCT typically ranges 0.10%–0.80% in normal conditions
- During major news events (CPI, Fed announcements, ETF news), ATR_PCT can spike above 1.5%+
- Consider time-of-day adjustments: Asian session tends to be LOW, US open tends to spike HIGH
